data.description: Quiet 55+ Community of Pine Run Estates ! This Willow model 2 bedroom 2 bath home is very well maintained including a NEW ROOF . Plenty of porch space in the front and the back to enjoy the breeze . The Front porch is full length and the back porch is screened in . Sprinkler system allowing for a lush yard and beautiful plants to thrive . There is also a bonus  Florida room that lets tons of natural light in and adds extra living space . The community has  2 club houses , pools, tennis courts and paved streets for an enjoyable golf cart ride . This would make a wonderful retirement home or a lovely 2nd home . Close to shopping, restaurants, hospitals, home improvement stores, movie theaters, etc on SR 200 and surrounding. Minutes to the New World Equestrian Center!!  Call for your appointment now ! Seller has a recent 4pt inspection .  HOA fees 132.00 per month .
